\mathcal{N}[g]=\sum_{k^{\prime}_\perp}\left(k^{\prime}_x k_y - k_x k^{\prime}_y  \right ) e^{-k^{\prime 2}_{\perp}/2} \phi_{k^{\prime}_\perp}g_{k_\perp-k^{\prime}_\perp}.
